Package io.odysz.semantic.DA

Class DatasetCfg

java.lang.Object
io.odysz.semantic.DA.DatasetCfg
public class DatasetCfg extends Object
Configured dataset.xml manager and helper.
- won't care using CP data source or DB manager (2019.2.28).
Author:
odys-z@github.com
